      "name": "Number C32: Shark Drake Leviathan",
      "effect": "4 Level 5 monsters\nYou can also Xyz Summon this card by discarding 1 Spell and using 1 Rank 4 \"Shark Drake\" Xyz Monster you control. (Transfer its materials to this card.) Once per turn (Quick Effect): You can detach 1 material from this card, then target 1 Effect Monster your opponent controls; negate its effects, and if you do, change its ATK/DEF to 0. This card can make a second attack during each Battle Phase, also if it attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage.",
      "official": false
    },
